OL,3,CDeaf Gladiator star hopes Peppa Pig
OL,4,Cepisode will help normalise condition
OL,6,FDewsbury-born Gladiator star Jodie
OL,7,FOunsley, also known at Fury, will
OL,8,Fenter the world of Peppa Pig as she
OL,9,Ftakes on the role of an audiologist in
OL,10,Fan upcoming episode about hearing loss.
OL,12,FThe animated children's television
OL,13,Fprogramme tells the story of Peppa who
OL,14,Flives with her family.
OL,16,FIt has been announced that a new
OL,17,Fstoryline will see her brother George
OL,18,Fdiagnosed as moderately deaf and
OL,19,Ffitted with a hearing aid.
