OL,3,CDeaf Gladiator star hopes Peppa Pig
OL,4,Cepisode will help normalise condition
OL,6,FJodie, known to fans as Fury, is
OL,7,Ftaking on the role of his audiologist.
OL,9,FThe 25-year-old athlete, who was born
OL,10,Fdeaf and had a cochlear implant as a
OL,11,Ftoddler, told ITV Calendar that it was
OL,12,F"an amazing project to be part of".
OL,14,FShe said: "I loved growing up with
OL,15,FPeppa Pig, so I never imagined me to
OL,16,Factually, for one, be a rugby player
OL,17,Fand then a Gladiator, and now an
OL,18,Fanimated audiologist. It's just
OL,19,Fbrilliant.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
