OL,3,CDeaf Gladiator star hopes Peppa Pig
OL,4,Cepisode will help normalise condition
OL,6,F"I can't help but think how much it
OL,7,Fcould impact kids watching it as well,
OL,8,Fbeing at such a young age and seeing a
OL,9,Fcharacter like George on TV."
OL,11,FShe also reflected on the lack of deaf
OL,12,Frole models in her childhood, saying:
OL,13,F"I have so many people who I looked up
OL,14,Fto when I was younger, especially like
OL,15,FOlympic athletes and my dad.
OL,17,F"I really was inspired by them, but I
OL,18,Fdidn't really know anyone who was deaf
OL,19,Fup until I was about 16, and that was
OL,20,Fbecause I competed in the Deaf
OL,21,FOlympics.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/4
