OL,3,CDeaf Gladiator star hopes Peppa Pig
OL,4,Cepisode will help normalise condition
OL,6,F"I don't think we can underestimate
OL,7,Fhow powerful it actually is, just by
OL,8,Fseeing someone on a TV show like this
OL,9,Fnormalises it in such a positive light.
OL,11,F"It gets people talking and starting
OL,12,Fthat conversation. Hopefully that make
OL,13,Fkids feel a bit more confident in
OL,14,Fthemselves."
OL,16,FThe upcoming storyline, which has been
OL,17,Fdeveloped in partnership with the
OL,18,FNational Deaf Children's Society, will
OL,19,Fair on Channel 5 Milkshake from 9
OL,20,FMarch.
